Title: Refundable Core Charge
meta_title: Refundable Core Charge for Vintage Mopar Parts
meta_description: Understand the refundable core charge for vintage Mopar parts. Get details on returning cores for credit.
product_description:
The Refundable Core Charge is an important part of the vintage auto parts process. When you purchase certain Mopar parts, you may be required to pay a core charge. This fee is a deposit that you can get back when you return your old, unusable part—also known as a core. This practice not only encourages recycling but also helps keep costs down for everyone involved.

To get your core charge refunded, simply return the old part in a condition that can be remanufactured. Make sure to follow any specific instructions provided at the time of purchase to ensure a smooth return process.
